item.title: CVE-2017-7634|2024-09-16T20:11:44.263Z -- qnap -- qnap%20media%20streaming%20add-on
item.description: Cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability in QNAP NAS application Media Streaming add-on version 421.1.0.2, 430.1.2.0, and earlier allows remote attackers to inject arbitrary web script or HTML. The injected code will only be triggered by a crafted link, not the normal page.
